name: Treasurer Robert Sprague
tweet: #DYK the cost of adoption can range from $10,000 to over $50,000?  Through our #FamilyForward program, Ohioans navigating the adoption process can access reduced interest loans to be used for qualified adoption expenses. ⤵️  https://t.co/qDdKnmAEdi

name: Treasurer Robert Sprague
tweet: @StableAccount offers greater financial independence to people living w/ disabilities. Some qualified expenses under the program include:  🏠 Housing  🚗 Transportation  📚 Education  💻 Assistive Technology and more!  Learn more:  https://t.co/kUvtDoaPqO  #DDAwareness22
